            <p class="mb-4">We print custom stickers and decals for businesses of all sizes throughout Joliet and the greater Chicagoland area. A well designed sticker is one of the most cost effective branding tools available. You can apply them to product packaging, hand them out at events, include them in order shipments, or use them to decorate your storefront windows and displays, and for larger window coverage our <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> department produces full-panel perforated vinyl that covers an entire glass surface with your brand. Breweries, restaurants, retail stores, and service companies across Will and DuPage County use our stickers to put their brand in the hands of their customers every single day, and many of our business clients pair their sticker orders with coordinating <a href="/promotional-items" class="link-notification">promotional items</a> like mugs and tote bags for a complete brand kit.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">We print on premium adhesive vinyl with an opaque backing that prevents background colors from showing through. Your design comes through crisp and true to color, whether you are printing on a light or dark sticker base. Our vinyl is air egress rated, which means you can reposition the sticker during application without leaving air bubbles behind, and for vehicle-specific applications that need professional-grade cast vinyl our <a href="/vehicle-graphics/dot-decals" class="link-notification">vehicle decals</a> team handles DOT compliance, fleet branding, and large-scale automotive graphics. It also does not tear as easily as standard paper stickers and it leaves no sticky residue when removed from most smooth surfaces.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">For a die-cut silhouette that matches your logo outline, see our <a href="/stickers/custom-shaped-stickers-decals" class="link-notification">custom shaped stickers</a>. For vehicle-specific application with professional-grade cast vinyl, explore our <a href="/vehicle-graphics/dot-decals" class="link-notification">vehicle decals and DOT decals</a>. For full-panel window coverage, our <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> offer perforated vinyl and large-format application.</p>
            <p>At <a href="/" class="link-notification">Top 5 Percent</a>, we offer adhesion levels from light grip for easy removal to permanent adhesion for long-term outdoor use. All stickers are weatherproof and hold up in rain, heat, and cold without fading or peeling. No minimums, so you can order exactly the quantity you need. Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> or visit 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet to get started.</p>
