                    <p>Call us at <a href="tel:+18153498600" class="link-notification">(815) 349-8600</a> or stop by our shop at 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet to talk about your sticker and decal needs. We are ready to help, and ask about pairing your sticker order with <a href="/promotional-items" class="link-notification">promotional items</a> for a complete branded giveaway kit.</p>
